{"tid":1439724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共 / 熱狗嘅新式分化攻擊？","createTime":"2019-08-10T08:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T08:16:16.000Z","uid":23170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44e460281902f739a56f654d4c0b025e54daa405","tid":1439724,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"前言：唔要大台係正解。<br />\n<br />\n不過有啲有心人將佢掉返轉槍頭攻擊返一堆明明無話要起大台嘅人，實施分化。我已經分唔清真心定假膠定係乜。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得用依招去瓦解仲嚟得快同方便，根本就係將要集成群嘅人都夾硬屈做大台，等我哋自己內部批鬥。<br />\n<br />\n就快前線企埋一堆又會俾人指住話佢哋要起大台。<br />\n<br />\n仲有連登已經被中共滲入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6LiRJZV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6LiRJZV.png&h=34840f28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QyRPvEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyRPvEV.png&h=fba3b020&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"014ec9e8457d21c5d4927037994baf67347c32bd","tid":1439724,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"大把支那狗mon post<br />\n只要團結<br />\n運動就可以繼續"},{"pid":"1987fa963e380bc46530ef6ee227fa79a569166b","tid":1439724,"uid":274475,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:03:51.000Z","msg":"近日突然出現巨量標題黨屌泛民屌大台Post，但泛民根本一直冇申個頭出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e15bd740d7be1c7e4b12974426c06536ba965a8","tid":1439724,"uid":281926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:15:40.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">It is now or never</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JbRLHyB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJbRLHyB.jpg&h=1e584e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0RU9pMh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http